{"id": "art-374", "label": "Art. 374", "title": "Art. 374: Pornografia infantilă", "slug": "art-374", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 374: Pornografia infantil&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1484382821\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1055\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1484382821\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Producerea, de&#355;inerea, procurarea, stocarea,\nexpunerea, promovarea, distribuirea, precum &#351;i punerea la dispozi&#355;ie,\nîn orice mod, de materiale pornografice cu minori se pedepsesc cu închisoarea\nde la 3 la 10 ani.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1317366891\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1054\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1317366891\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>1</sup>)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Cu\npedeapsa prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) se pedepse&#351;te &#351;i îndemnarea\nsau recrutarea unui minor în scopul particip&#259;rii lui în cadrul unui\nspectacol pornografic, ob&#355;inerea de foloase de pe urma unui astfel de\nspectacol în cadrul c&#259;ruia particip&#259; minori sau exploatarea unui\nminor în orice altfel pentru realizarea de spectacole pornografice.</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) Conform art. II din Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>217/2020</span><span style='color:black'>, prin\nexcep&#355;ie de la prevederile art. 9 din Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>286/2009</span><span style='color:black'> privind Codul\npenal, publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea I, nr. 510 din\n24 iulie 2009, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile ulterioare,\n&#351;i în aplicarea art. 12 din Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>286/2009</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile\nulterioare, pentru faptele prev&#259;zute la art. 218-220, art. 221 alin.\n(1)-(2<sup>1</sup>), art. 222<sup>1</sup>, art. 216<sup>1</sup> &#351;i art.\n374 alin. (1) &#351;i (1<sup>1</sup>) din Legea nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>286/2009</span><span style='color:black'>, cu\nmodific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile ulterioare, legea penal&#259;\nromân&#259; se aplic&#259; infrac&#355;iunilor s&#259;vâr&#351;ite în afara\nteritoriului &#355;&#259;rii de c&#259;tre un cet&#259;&#355;ean român sau de o\npersoan&#259; juridic&#259; român&#259; indiferent de pedeapsa prev&#259;zut&#259;\nde legea român&#259;, chiar dac&#259; fapta nu este prev&#259;zut&#259; ca\ninfrac&#355;iune de legea penal&#259; a &#355;&#259;rii unde aceasta a fost\ns&#259;vâr&#351;it&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_146951660\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1053\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_146951660\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1<sup>2</sup>)Vizionarea de spectacole pornografice în\ncadrul c&#259;rora particip&#259; minori se pedepse&#351;te cu închisoare de la\nun an la 5 ani.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1255749453\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1052\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1255749453\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dac&#259; faptele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) au fost\ns&#259;vâr&#351;ite printr-un sistem informatic sau alt mijloc de stocare a\ndatelor informatice, pedeapsa este închisoarea de la 5 la 12 ani.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2123884517\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1051\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2123884517\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Accesarea, f&#259;r&#259; drept, de materiale\npornografice cu minori, prin intermediul sistemelor informatice sau altor\nmijloace de comunica&#355;ii electronice, se pedepse&#351;te cu închisoare de\nla unu la 3 ani.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1117253413\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1050\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1117253413\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>1</sup>)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Dac&#259;\nfaptele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1), (1<sup>1</sup>), (1<sup>2</sup>) &#351;i\n(2) au fost s&#259;vâr&#351;ite în urm&#259;toarele împrejur&#259;ri:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1501798598\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1049\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1501798598\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)de c&#259;tre un membru de familie sau de c&#259;tre o\npersoan&#259; care convie&#355;uie&#351;te cu victima;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2003552236\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1048\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2003552236\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)de c&#259;tre o persoan&#259; în a c&#259;rei îngrijire,\nocrotire, educare, paz&#259; sau tratament se afla minorul sau de o\npersoan&#259; care a abuzat de pozi&#355;ia sa recunoscut&#259; de încredere\nsau de autoritate asupra minorului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1615589659\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1047\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1615589659\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)fapta a pus în pericol via&#355;a minorului;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_662566649\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1046\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_662566649\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)de c&#259;tre o persoan&#259; care a mai comis anterior o\ninfrac&#355;iune contra libert&#259;&#355;ii &#351;i integrit&#259;&#355;ii\nsexuale asupra unui minor, o infrac&#355;iune de pornografie infantil&#259; sau\nproxenetism asupra unui minor, limitele speciale ale pedepselor se\nmajoreaz&#259; cu o treime.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_196025411\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1045\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_196025411\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>2</sup>)Fapta unui major de a solicita unui minor\ns&#259; înregistreze, s&#259; produc&#259;, s&#259; distribuie, s&#259;\nexpun&#259; sau s&#259; transmit&#259; prin orice mijloace, inclusiv prin\nmijloace de comunica&#355;ii electronice sau pe re&#355;ele sociale, imagini,\nvideoclipuri sau alte materiale pornografice care îl prezint&#259; pe minorul\nrespectiv având un comportament sexual explicit sau care, de&#351;i nu\nprezint&#259; o persoan&#259; real&#259;, simuleaz&#259;, în mod credibil, un\nminor având un astfel de comportament, precum &#351;i orice reprezentare a\norganelor genitale ale unui copil cu scop sexual se pedepse&#351;te cu\nînchisoare de la 5 la 12 ani.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_19601898\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1044\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_19601898\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>materiale\npornografice cu minori</i> se în&#355;elege orice material care prezint&#259;\nun minor ori o persoan&#259; major&#259; drept un minor, având un comportament\nsexual explicit sau care, de&#351;i nu prezint&#259; o persoan&#259;\nreal&#259;, simuleaz&#259;, în mod credibil, un minor având un astfel de\ncomportament, precum &#351;i orice reprezentare a organelor genitale ale unui\ncopil cu scop sexual.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_669093568\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1043\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Penal.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_669093568\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4<sup>1</sup>)Prin <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>spectacol\npornografic</i> se în&#355;elege expunerea în direct adresat&#259; unui public,\ninclusiv prin tehnologia informa&#355;iilor &#351;i comunica&#355;iilor, a unui\ncopil implicat într-un comportament sexual explicit ori a organelor genitale\nale unui copil, cu scop sexual.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)Tentativa se pedepse&#351;te.</span></p>"}